{"tid":1710161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成立罷交稅大聯盟 二百萬人同一陣線","createTime":"2019-11-12T05:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T07:14:12.000Z","uid":167938,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1360bf46cb5a5ce0e614e3ec736fe4fb954bf168","tid":1710161,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:49:32.000Z","msg":"啲大陸豬搵得雞碎咁多要我地養<br />\n養撚完仲要用我地啲錢打鳩我地仔女<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我宣布2019-2020年罷交薪俸稅大聯盟正式成立</span></span><br />\n<br />\n誠邀會計師 律師專業人士比意見<br />\n點樣可以組織呢個大行動 迫使政府含撚<br />\n<br />\n一齊告鳩我地二百萬人<br />\n監獄有無咁多位<br />\n<br />\n無我地呢班交稅養你班狗 你有水飲有飯食？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wpif6qF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWpif6qF.png&h=b04c457e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佔政府大約10%收入<br />\n但而家樓市低迷 賣地無人買<br />\n做生意既人收入下跌<br />\n<br />\n打工仔出糧先係最穩既根基<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"3dbf7e01c4cd74b42bb9d4d70b3d53e9cf089814","tid":1710161,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:51:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8fbbd0fbe0225135c02098fad0f3820ea8772be3","tid":1710161,"uid":7555,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58da24283dce2770aed85e868fd05c2c5de125f8","tid":1710161,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:51:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ef60fcd8ede82b89d427dc8fb24f97318a563da","tid":1710161,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:51:47.000Z","msg":"無交幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03abefe283